&lt;p&gt;Creative intelligence wasn&amp;rsquo;t inevitable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now, that&amp;rsquo;s one argument, and we have to be humble in the face of uncertainty here because no one knows. But I want to give an argument that rarely gets any air time.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>If You’re So Smart, Why Aren’t You Happy?</title><link>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2020 15:02:38 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/naval/orig/if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/naval/zh/if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
