&lt;h1 id="is-it-worth-being-wise"&gt;Is It Worth Being Wise?&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;February 2007&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A few days ago I finally figured out something I&amp;rsquo;ve wondered about for 25 years: the relationship between wisdom and intelligence. Anyone can see they&amp;rsquo;re not the same by the number of people who are smart, but not very wise. And yet intelligence and wisdom do seem related. How?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Why Nerds are Unpopular</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/nerds/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/nerds/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/nerds/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
